Clone the Repository Locally:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/chaintrust.git
cd chaintrust
//
//
//
Create the Project Structure:
mkdir client server contracts
//
//
//
Set Up the Client:
Navigate to the client directory and create a React app.
cd client
npx create-react-app .
npm install web3
//
//
//
Set Up the Server:
Navigate to the server directory and initialize a Node.js project
cd ../server
npm init -y
npm install express mongoose cors
//
//
//
Set Up Smart Contracts:
navigate to the contracts directory and set up Truffle.
cd ../contracts
npm init -y
npm install truffle
npx truffle init

